# KitfoxPay — 唯一需要的环境变量 / The only environment variable needed
#
# 所有其他配置（Jeepay、Paystack、服务器、管理密码等）通过管理界面 localhost:9219 设置。
# All other config is set via the admin UI at localhost:9219 — no env vars needed for those.
#
# DATABASE_URL — PostgreSQL 连接字符串（可选）/ PostgreSQL connection string (optional)
# 用途：Webhook 幂等性持久化（防止支付重复处理）
# Purpose: persistent webhook idempotency (prevents duplicate payment processing)
#
# 不设置 → 自动退回内存模式（功能正常，但重启后幂等性失效）
# Not set → falls back to memory mode (works fine, idempotency just resets on restart)
#
# 兼容任何 PostgreSQL 提供商 / Works with any PostgreSQL provider:
#
#   Supabase  → Dashboard → Project Settings → Database → Connection String → URI
#   Aiven     → Service Overview → Connection Information → Service URI
#   Neon      → Dashboard → Connection Details → Connection string
#   Railway   → Service → Variables → DATABASE_URL (已自动注入 / auto-injected)
#   本地      → postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/kitfoxpay
#
# 在 Render 上设置 / Setting on Render:
#   Dashboard → Your Service → Environment → Add Environment Variable
#   Key:   DATABASE_URL
#   Value: (粘贴连接字符串 / paste connection string)
#
# 首次启动时自动建表，无需手动执行任何 SQL。
# Table is created automatically on first run — no manual SQL needed.

DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@host:5432/dbname
